                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1252" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0113</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10445 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">S外资仪器公司两位总经理的领导风格</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Comparison of Two General Managers’ Leadership in S Foreign Instrument Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孔文，王立荣等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">S外资仪器公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仪器、仪表工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外资企业，仪器公司，变革型领导，交易型领导，组织变革；2013百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Foreign company, Instrument Company, Transactional leadership, Transformational leadership, Organizational changes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自20世纪末至今，面对经济全球化和科技的迅猛发展，企业竞争日益激烈。环境变化给管理者和领导者带来严峻的挑战和考验。面对组织变革的迫切需要，变革型领导方式能够带来一定的启示。本案例依据变革型领导和交易型领导理论，以S外资仪器公司为背景，描述了公司在发生重大组织变革前后，两位总经理截然不同的领导风格对企业和员工所带来的变化和影响。通过对比变革型和交易型两种领导风格，着重诠释了变革型领导方式如何成功地推动组织变革。本案例分为两个部分：第一部分为案例正文，以时间先后顺序分别介绍了S集团公司总经理Jack领导时发生的“货物失踪事件”、“突如其来的表扬”、“Jack的困惑”和“面临‘解体’的销售团队”四个事件；Tony领导时如何实现“理念重塑”、“员工激励”，以及“强将手下无弱兵”、“销售渠道变革”和“金融危机来临”五个事件。第二部分为案例使用说明，主要利用交易型和变革型领导方式相关理论对Jack和Tony的领导风格进行了分析和对比，探讨变革型领导成功的要素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the end of 20 century, the enterprise competition is getting increasingly fierce with economic globalization and technological development. Managers and leaders are facing severe challenges with the changes of environment. Faced the urgent demand of organizational changes, transformational leadership will bring us some enlightenment.Based on theory of transformational and transactional leadership which was proposed by Burns(1978) and Bernard M. Bass(1981,1985), this case focuses on how two general managers changed and affected the company and employees with different leadership when organizational changes took place in S foreign instrument company. This case mainly explains how transformational leadership succeeded in implementing organization changes with comparison of two leadership.The case consists of two parts. The first part is the case text, it introduces events in time sequence when two general managers led S Group Ltd. First, it introduces the missing of goods, unexpectedly praise, Jack’s confusion and the disintegration of sales team when Jack led the company. Second, it introduces how Tony realize transformation in remolding philosophy, inspiriting employees, ‘an able leader will make a company of good followers’, ‘sales channel transformation’ and ‘financial crisis is coming’ when Tony led the company. The second part is the case instruction, it mainly uses relevant theories of transactional and transformational leadership to analyze and contrast two general managers’ leadership and explores the elements that transformational leader succeeds.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2008</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《领导学》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">领导风格及组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
